OL,5, Macau gambling kingpin Alvin Chau has  
OL,6, been sentenced to 18 years in jail for 
OL,7, more than 100 charges including        
OL,8, organised crime and illegal gaming.    
OL,10,FThe 48-year-old was found guilty in a  
OL,11,Fcase that centred on illegal bets      
OL,12,Fexceeding HK$823.7bn (#85.7bn; $105bn).
OL,14,FChau, a high-profile and colourful     
OL,15,Ffigure in the local casino industry,   
OL,16,Fhad denied the charges.                
OL,18,FMacau, a former Portuguese colony, is  
OL,19,Fthe only Chinese city where gambling is
OL,20,Flegal.                                 
